<div class="res-text richtextContent background-hidden" id="372f2c31-443e-4b04-acbc-4cd92d034b01" >

    <p>Course mailing lists are offered to facilitate communication between Ryerson's faculty and their students. An instructor can request a list for a course/section they are currently teaching. These lists can be used for the distribution of information and also for online discussions with students.&nbsp;</p> 
<p>The Groups are active for the terms the course is running, e.g. for a two term course, if the instructor chose the two term option at the time of requesting the list, the list will be active for two terms. &nbsp;</p> 
<p>Click the links below for more information on Google Groups and how to request a course mailing list.</p> 
<p><a href="/content/ryerson/google/getting-started/google-groups/guide.html">Google Groups</a></p> 
<p><a href="/content/ryerson/google/getting-started/google-groups/guide.html#accordion-1499193754905-filling-a-course-mailing-list-request">How to request a course mailing list</a></p>
    





</div>
